OL,7,FIn a Green Paper due to be published
OL,8,Falongside Mr Stride's statement,
OL,9,Fministers will set out plans to reform
OL,10,Fpersonal independence payments (PIP) -
OL,11,Fthe main disability benefit - through
OL,12,Fchanges to eligibility criteria and
OL,13,Fassessments.
OL,15,FThe government says the proposals are
OL,16,Faimed at providing "more tailored
OL,17,Fsupport in line with their needs" but
OL,18,Fopposition MPs and charities have hit
OL,19,Fout at the plans, with Scope calling
OL,20,Fthem a "reckless assault" on disabled
OL,21,Fpeople.
