OL,7,FA consultation on the plans will run
OL,8,Ffor 12 weeks, closing on July 23.
OL,10,FThe government hopes the overall
OL,11,Fimpact will be to move to a system
OL,12,Fwhere PIP is more geared towards
OL,13,Fcovering the actual extra costs faced
OL,14,Fby people with disabilities.
OL,16,FJames Taylor, the executive director
OL,17,Fof strategy at disability equity
OL,18,Fcharity Scope, called for an end to
OL,19,Fthe "reckless assault" on disabled
OL,20,Fpeople and to fix the "real underlying
OL,21,Fissues".
